name: Jade - Dragon Quest XI
description:
Another slight departure from the 3 series girls. I imagine anyone that likes what I've made so far may have perhaps anticipated this. lol

Tag: jade (dq11)

Like always, I cannot guarantee you'll get amazing results, but hopefully you'll find the model worth your time.

Trained in: NAI

Sample images are all Kotos.

Best weight to use is around: 0.8-1. I didn't test this one nearly as much! It was a pretty quick production.

This was all generated via Colab!

Anomalies:

  • Nothing that I'm too aware of. Didn't do any testing on holding a weapon, so hopefully it works for you!
